57 #define WATCHDOG0_RIS_R (*((volatile unsigned long *)0x40000010))

59 #define WATCHDOG0_TEST_R (*((volatile unsigned long *)0x40000418))
60 #define WATCHDOG0_LOCK_R (*((volatile unsigned long *)0x40000C00))

8292 //*****************************************************************************
8293 //
8294 // The following are defines for the bit fields in the UDMA_STAT register.
8295 //
8296 //*****************************************************************************
8297 #define UDMA_STAT_DMACHANS_M 0x001F0000 // Available uDMA Channels Minus 1
8298 #define UDMA_STAT_STATE_M 0x000000F0 // Control State Machine Status
8299 #define UDMA_STAT_STATE_IDLE 0x00000000 // Idle
8300 #define UDMA_STAT_STATE_RD_CTRL 0x00000010 // Reading channel controller data
8301 #define UDMA_STAT_STATE_RD_SRCENDP \
8302  0x00000020 // Reading source end pointer
8303 #define UDMA_STAT_STATE_RD_DSTENDP \
8304  0x00000030 // Reading destination end pointer
8305 #define UDMA_STAT_STATE_RD_SRCDAT \
8306  0x00000040 // Reading source data
8307 #define UDMA_STAT_STATE_WR_DSTDAT \
8308  0x00000050 // Writing destination data
8309 #define UDMA_STAT_STATE_WAIT 0x00000060 // Waiting for uDMA request to
8310  // clear
